{"tid":1453121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：很多人不明白，我們面對的是一個專政體系（totalitarian regime）。","createTime":"2019-08-12T03:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:43:05.000Z","uid":107060,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5082239072c6dcd0e7052610b01fe3381f52d4a2","tid":1453121,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:18:00.000Z","msg":"陳雲：很多人不明白，我們面對的是一個專政體系（totalitarian regime）。我與這個源自蘇維埃的專政體系，周旋了三十幾年。各位不信我的，結果有今日。<br />\n源自前蘇聯的俄羅斯外交部發言之後，香港就出現昨晚的血腥鎮壓，港共政府露出蘇維埃政府的本性。莫斯科的蘇維埃與北京的蘇維埃合流，令香港人見識清楚，我們面對的是一個專政體系。<br />\n我曾經帶你們見到真相的，也曾經帶你們如何在安全的環境完成香港自治。<br />\n香港是西柏林，我們站在自由民主憲政那邊。但請你老實認識清楚，我們面對的是一個蘇維埃政權（soviet regime）。而香港人背棄過我的鬥爭方法，至今仍在誣衊我。<br />\n潛伏。讀書是武裝思想，也是靈性救贖。請各位讀好《香港城邦論》。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/commerce/products/1537897132904577/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcommerce%2Fproducts%2F1537897132904577%2F&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpAjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=39b5b206\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/commerce/products/1537897132904577/</a>"},{"pid":"1a93bbf3a086ebaf5260564339c2a046b587534c","tid":1453121,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:21:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a3d4d2cfdcd2d7476ac16dddf1cab24cc9ceb3","tid":1453121,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab61a5d1042563f5bb781ef181d009afffb5e94","tid":1453121,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:05:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b795c5618ee287a851469f057eaa5334091ad916","tid":1453121,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile